### ─── Auth ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Register
POST http://localhost:8081/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Anas",
  "email": "anas@contractpulse.com",
  "password": "password123"
}

### Login
POST http://localhost:8081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "anas@contractpulse.com",
  "password": "password123"
}
### TEST Login
POST http://localhost:8081/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Anas",
  "email": "anas@test.com",
  "password": "temp"
}

### ─── Clients ────────────────────────────────────────────

### Create client
POST http://localhost:8081/api/clients
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Ahmed Khan",
  "email": "ahmed@example.com",
  "phone": "0300-1234567"
}

### Get all clients
GET http://localhost:8081/api/clients
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get client by ID
GET http://localhost:8081/api/clients/{{clientId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update client
PUT http://localhost:8081/api/clients/{{clientId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Ahmed Khan Updated",
  "email": "ahmed.updated@example.com",
  "phone": "0300-9999999"
}

### Delete client
DELETE http://localhost:8081/api/clients/{{clientId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ─── Contracts ──────────────────────────────────────────

### Create contract
POST http://localhost:8081/api/contracts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "E-Commerce Website",
  "description": "Full stack website for clothing brand",
  "clientId": "{{clientId}}",
  "totalValue": 150000.00,
  "startDate": "2025-04-01",
  "endDate": "2025-06-30"
}

### Get all contracts
GET http://localhost:8081/api/contracts
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get contract by ID
GET http://localhost:8081/api/contracts/{{contractId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update contract status
PATCH http://localhost:8081/api/contracts/{{contractId}}/status?status=ACTIVE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Delete contract
DELETE http://localhost:8081/api/contracts/{{contractId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ─── Milestones ─────────────────────────────────────────

### Create milestone
POST http://localhost:8081/api/contracts/{{contractId}}/milestones
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "UI Design & Wireframes",
  "amount": 30000.00,
  "dueDate": "2025-04-15",
  "orderIndex": 1
}

### Create milestone 2
POST http://localhost:8081/api/contracts/{{contractId}}/milestones
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Backend APIs",
  "amount": 70000.00,
  "dueDate": "2025-05-30",
  "orderIndex": 2
}

### Get all milestones
GET http://localhost:8081/api/contracts/{{contractId}}/milestones
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Update milestone status
PATCH http://localhost:8081/api/contracts/{{contractId}}/milestones/{{milestoneId}}/status?status=IN_PROGRESS
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ─── Invoices ───────────────────────────────────────────

### Generate invoice for milestone
POST http://localhost:8081/api/invoices/generate/{{milestoneId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Get invoice by ID
GET http://localhost:8081/api/invoices/{{invoiceId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Mark invoice as paid
PATCH http://localhost:8081/api/invoices/{{invoiceId}}/status?status=PAID
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ─── Portal (public - no auth) ─────────────────────────

### View client portal
GET http://localhost:8081/api/portal/{{publicToken}}
### AI
GET http://localhost:8081/api/ai/summary/{{contractId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###PDF
GET http://localhost:8081/api/invoices/{{invoiceId}}/pdf
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}